<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <style>
      * {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        box-sizing: border-box;
      }
      body {
        font-family: Georgia, serif;
        background-color: #f8f8f8;
      }
      .container {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 20px;
        background-color: #ffffff;
        box-shadow: 0px 0px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      }
      .header {
        text-align: center;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
      }
      .logo {
        width: 100px;
        height: 100px;
        margin-bottom: 10px;
      }
      .title {
        font-size: 24px;
        font-weight: bold;
        color: #333333;
      }
      .content {
        margin-bottom: 20px;
      }
      .message {
        margin-bottom: 10px;
        color: #555555;
        line-height: 1.5;
      }
      .sender {
        font-weight: bold;
        color: #333333;
      }
      .footer {
        text-align: center;
        color: #888888;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="header">
        <h1 class="title">Welcome to Solitaro</h1>
      </div>
      <div class="content">
        <p class="message">
          Hey there, <b><%= username %>!</b>
        </p>
        <p class="message">
          Welcome to Solitaro, where digital adventures reach new heights!
          Discover captivating content, connect with awesome people, and let
          your talents shine. Solitaro is not just another social media
          platform; it's your vibrant community where friendships bloom,
          curiosity runs wild, and laughter knows no bounds. Get ready to dive
          in, explore, and flourish like a true Solitaro champ.
        </p>
        <p class="message">
          We can't wait to see the magic you'll bring to our fantastic
          community.
        </p>
        <p class="message">
          Best regards,
          <br>
          <span class="sender"><%= sender %></span>
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="footer">
        <p>&copy; 2023 Solitaro. All rights reserved.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
